OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,FThe powerful voice and trailblazing
OL,7,Fcareer of the 'Total Eclipse of the
OL,8,FHeart' singer has been warmly
OL,9,Fremembered, as ITV News Arts Editor
OL,10,FNina Nannar reports
OL,12,FTributes are pouring in for Bonnie
OL,13,FTyler after her family announced
OL,14,FThursday that the Welsh singer has
OL,15,Fdied, aged 75.
OL,17,FTyler had previously been placed in an
OL,18,Finduced coma after having emergency
OL,19,Fintestinal surgery near her home in
OL,20,FFaro, Portugal, in May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
