OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783711191
OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,FIn June, her spokesperson said the
OL,7,FWelsh-born star was "no longer in a
OL,8,Fcoma" but remained "very unwell" and
OL,9,Fin intensive care.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, a message from her family
OL,12,Fon the singer's website said:
OL,13,F"Bonnie's family and team are
OL,14,Fheartbroken to announce that Bonnie
OL,15,Funexpectedly passed away last night in
OL,16,Fhospital in Portugal as a result of
OL,17,Fthe illness that she was being treated
OL,18,Ffrom."
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@EO]pD@TOUpD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
