CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783711191
OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,F"An iconic figure, she leaves behind a
OL,7,Fcatalogue of music ` from Total
OL,8,FEclipse Of The Heart to Holding Out
OL,9,FFor A Hero ` which continues to touch
OL,10,Flives, flood dance floors and fill
OL,11,Fkaraoke booths," the PM's official
OL,12,Fspokesperson said.
OL,14,FAlso paying tribute was Sir Cliff
OL,15,FRichard, who wrote that she was a
OL,16,F"wonderful friend gone too soon".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@PO]xD@AOUxD@`O]
