OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,FIn a post shared on Facebook, he said:
OL,7,F"Bonnie's infectious zest for life
OL,8,Fentertained so many around the world,
OL,9,Fand to be a good friend to all,
OL,10,Fincluding me.
OL,12,F"It is shocking news to wake up to
OL,13,Fthis morning and I send my love to her
OL,14,Ffamily at this very sad time."
OL,16,FSir Rod Stewart, Spandau Ballet
OL,17,Ffrontman Tony Hadley and Doctor Who
OL,18,Fshowrunner Russell T Davies are among
OL,19,Fthe stars who added to tributes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
