OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,FPop star Sir Rod referenced his live
OL,7,Fcover of one of Tyler's hits in a post
OL,8,Fon Instagram: "We shared similar
OL,9,Fstyles of vocalising.
OL,11,F"She was a good pal, a true soul
OL,12,Fstirrer.
OL,14,F"I sing It's A Heartache every night
OL,15,Fon tour. I'll miss you darling Bonnie."
OL,17,FHadley said of Tyler on X: "She was an
OL,18,Fincredible woman, so kind and friendly
OL,19,Fto me as a young artist. Over the
OL,20,Fyears, we met several times and she
OL,21,Fwas always the same Bonnie.
OL,26,@pD@OOUsD@AOUvD@AOUwD@gO]yD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
