PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783711191
OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,F"Her voice was truly amazing and
OL,7,Fstanding next to her you really got to
OL,8,Ffeel her power. A beautiful legend."
OL,10,FMeanwhile, Doctor Who showrunner
OL,11,FDavies praised the "fabulous" singer
OL,12,Fwhom he had "loved" since his teens.
OL,14,FTyler, whose real name is Gaynor
OL,15,FHopkins, rocketed to international
OL,16,Ffame in the 1980s, with the release of
OL,17,Fher hit single Total Eclipse Of The
OL,18,FHeart which shot to the top of the
OL,19,Fcharts in the UK and US.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@dO]sD@TOUsD@]O]tD@MOUtD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
