OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,FRecognisable for her husky voice,
OL,7,FTyler has released many hit songs over
OL,8,Fthe years, including Holding Out For A
OL,9,FHero, It's A Heartache and If You Were
OL,10,FA Woman (And I Was A Man).
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe Grammy-nominated star was also due
OL,18,Fto tour Europe later this year to mark
OL,19,F50 years since the release of her 1976
OL,20,Fbreakthrough hit, Lost In France,
OL,21,Fwhich entered the charts across Europe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
