PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783711191
OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,FTyler was scheduled to perform in
OL,7,FMalta and Germany, and her upcoming
OL,8,Ftour also included shows across the
OL,9,FUK, as well as in Austria, Hungary,
OL,10,FTurkey and Romania.
OL,12,FThe singer also represented the UK in
OL,13,Fthe 2013 Eurovision Song Contest in
OL,14,FMalmo, Sweden, with the song Believe
OL,15,FIn Me, finishing in 19th place.
OL,17,FShe was made an MBE in 2023 for her
OL,18,Fservices to music, after being named
OL,19,Fin the Queen's Birthday Honours list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
