PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783711191
OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,FIt was there that she gave her first
OL,7,Fpublic performance as child with a
OL,8,Frendition of the hymn All Things
OL,9,FBright And Beautiful.
OL,11,FHaving left school at 16 with no
OL,12,Fqualifications, in 1969 she was
OL,13,Fentered into a local talent contest by
OL,14,Fan aunt, finishing second.
OL,16,FAlthough the prize money was just #1,
OL,17,Fshe was encouraged by her success to
OL,18,Fpursue a career in music, initially
OL,19,Ffinding work as a backing singer with
OL,20,FBobby Wayne and the Dixies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
