PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783711191
OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,FIn 1975 Tyler was spotted performing
OL,7,Fin the Townsman Club in Swansea by
OL,8,Ftalent scout Roger Bell who invited
OL,9,Fher to London to record a demo tape,
OL,10,Fand months later she was offered her
OL,11,Ffirst recording contract by RCA who
OL,12,Fadvised her to change her name.
OL,14,FHer debut single My! My! Honeycomb
OL,15,Fdidn't perform well, but the follow-up
OL,16,F` Lost In France ` became her first
OL,17,Fhit, reaching number nine in the UK
OL,18,Fsingles chart, leading to her debut
OL,19,Fappearance on Top Of The Pops.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783711191
OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,FIt was after this hit that she began
OL,7,Fto develop a sore throat, and was told
OL,8,Fshe had developed nodules on her vocal
OL,9,Fcords, leading to them being
OL,10,Fsurgically removed.
OL,12,FOnce the operation was done, Tyler was
OL,13,Fadvised to rest her voice completely
OL,14,Ffor six weeks, which she could not do.
OL,16,FShe was later told she may have
OL,17,Fsuffered permanent damage when her
OL,18,Fvoice developed a gravelly rasp - but
OL,19,Fher producers loved it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
