PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783711191
OL,3,C'One of Britain's greatest': Tributes
OL,4,Cpour in after death of Bonnie Tyler
OL,6,F"When I went into the studio they all
OL,7,Fsaid, 'Bloody 'ell, where's that voice
OL,8,Fcome from?' I now sounded like a
OL,9,Ffemale Rod Stewart," Tyler said.
OL,11,FSix years later, her new trademark
OL,12,Fsound found its perfect setting on
OL,13,FTotal Eclipse Of The Heart, a soaring,
OL,14,Fover-the-top power ballad that topped
OL,15,Fthe charts on both sides of the
OL,16,FAtlantic.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
